/* Determining the year Jesus was born */ I included a phrase which shows why some Christians think that we have misunderstood and mistranslated Luke's text. These men are are significant leaders, with massive audiences.

/* Determining the year Jesus was born */ I included a phrase, which affirms the 3/2 dates for Jesus' birth as per the section above about the 3/2 conjunction theories, which being right or wrong, are exceedingly widespread.

/* Determining the year Jesus was born */ Included the adjective "Most modern scholars" instead of "Modern scholars." As indicated earlier in the paragraph, there are different opinions held by influential "modern scholars."

/* Determining the year Jesus was born */ A reference to Steinmann's work was placed almost as though he supported a 4 BC date for Herod's death. Right or wrong, he supports a 1 BC date for Herod's death with several other scholars as now indicated.
